{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020-07-15-write-github-about-with-readme-file/","result":{"data":{"site":{"id":"Site","siteMetadata":{"title":"Will Lai - Programming!","siteUrl":"https://willlaiwk.github.io"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"cec842ad-e6c4-5bd7-bf69-a8b39cffd395","excerpt":"最近 Github 悄悄地釋出了一個新功能， 可以讓你在個人首頁中透過 Markdown 文件，顯示自己的個人化資訊。 成果圖大概長這樣:  下面就讓我們來看看如何實作吧！ 建立神秘的 Repository 首先我們進入建立 Repository…","html":"<p>最近 Github 悄悄地釋出了一個新功能，</p>\n<p>可以讓你在個人首頁中透過 Markdown 文件，顯示自己的個人化資訊。</p>\n<p>成果圖大概長這樣:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/835b95607e8a2c41965e2b6049ab8297/0ffd9/home-page.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.504300234558244%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"成果\"\n        title=\"成果\"\n        src=\"/static/835b95607e8a2c41965e2b6049ab8297/5a190/home-page.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/835b95607e8a2c41965e2b6049ab8297/772e8/home-page.png 200w,\n/static/835b95607e8a2c41965e2b6049ab8297/e17e5/home-page.png 400w,\n/static/835b95607e8a2c41965e2b6049ab8297/5a190/home-page.png 800w,\n/static/835b95607e8a2c41965e2b6049ab8297/c1b63/home-page.png 1200w,\n/static/835b95607e8a2c41965e2b6049ab8297/29007/home-page.png 1600w,\n/static/835b95607e8a2c41965e2b6049ab8297/0ffd9/home-page.png 2558w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>下面就讓我們來看看如何實作吧！</p>\n<h2>建立神秘的 Repository</h2>\n<p>首先我們進入建立 Repository 的頁面，並在 <code class=\"language-text\">Repository name</code> 中輸入與 <code class=\"language-text\">Owner</code> 一樣的名字，接下來就會看到下圖中 Github 所顯示的彩蛋文字囉!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/39d1902aa9a84ad09ba9ede52f4e9b16/80cfc/create-repo.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.68980477223427%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"create repo\"\n        title=\"create repo\"\n        src=\"/static/39d1902aa9a84ad09ba9ede52f4e9b16/5a190/create-repo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/39d1902aa9a84ad09ba9ede52f4e9b16/772e8/create-repo.png 200w,\n/static/39d1902aa9a84ad09ba9ede52f4e9b16/e17e5/create-repo.png 400w,\n/static/39d1902aa9a84ad09ba9ede52f4e9b16/5a190/create-repo.png 800w,\n/static/39d1902aa9a84ad09ba9ede52f4e9b16/c1b63/create-repo.png 1200w,\n/static/39d1902aa9a84ad09ba9ede52f4e9b16/29007/create-repo.png 1600w,\n/static/39d1902aa9a84ad09ba9ede52f4e9b16/80cfc/create-repo.png 1844w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>建立完成後，在這 Repository 中的根目錄建立 <code class=\"language-text\">README.md</code>，然後其內容就會顯示在你的個人首頁中囉～</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"如何客製化 Github 個人資訊首頁","date":"July 15, 2020","description":"最近 Github 悄悄地釋出了一個新功能。可以讓你在個人首頁中透過 Markdown 文件，顯示自己的個人化資訊..."}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020-07-15-write-github-abou